headers.subject: [tosdr:2541] Instagram statute of limitation on claims

html:
You agree that any claim you may have arising out of or related to your relationship with Instagram must be filed within one year after such claim arose; otherwise, your claim is permanently barred.

http://instagram.com/about/legal/terms/

Title: You have one year to bring a claim

Topic: governance

Summary: Any claim that you have related to Instagram has to be filed within a year after the claim arose. If not, that claim is permanently barred, meaning you can't bring it against Instagram.

Score: 50 (mediocre)
